1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,870
Some evenings are too important to miss.
有些傍晚，值得再次走出去。

2
00:00:02,870 --> 00:00:06,650
A steady ride makes room for quieter, better moments.
稳定前行，才能把时间留给更好的陪伴。

3
00:00:06,650 --> 00:00:10,310
Sometimes the real luxury is simply being there together.
真正珍贵的，是还能一起站在风景里。

4
00:00:10,310 --> 00:00:13,150
Beyond mobility. We defend dignity.
超越移动，我们守护尊严。
